{"tid":401829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"倫敦政治經濟學院支持周永康","createTime":"2017-09-16T02:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T03:21:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11c66e107d77862c32339662f4dfb1b38fef309e","tid":401829,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:54:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20154609&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170916\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20154609%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170916&d=2eCDVJIknrktphmt0Xw3UpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=e1d63b40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20154609%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170916&h=08a79f60\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20154609&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170916</a><br />\n<br />\n倫敦政治經濟學院支持周永康<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170916/large/16la7p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170916%2Flarge%2F16la7p10.jpg&h=73381811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周永康早前因重奪公民廣場案被判囚。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】雙學三子包括黃之鋒、羅冠聰及周永康因重奪公民廣場一案被判囚，其中周永康就讀的倫敦政治經濟學院（LSE）發表聲明，指該校師生非常關心周永康的情況，讚揚周在學期間對學校有非常正面的貢獻，校內師生均對他有非常高的評價，已向英國政府及香港部門了解周的情況，會提供一切可行支援，並確保周能完成學業。<br />\n<br />\n學者促放三子<br />\n<br />\n被上訴庭判囚7個月的周永康，原於LSE修讀碩士課程，其學校管理委員會早前召開會議，並發表聲明，指周因2014年的民主運動被判囚，校方非常關注他的情況，會向有關部門了解確保其福祉。<br />\n<br />\n此外，36名來自世界各地包括香港、英國、美國、德國、法國、澳洲、南非等地的學者，聯署要求港府釋放周永康、黃之鋒及羅冠聰，包括中文大學教授Gordon Mathews、LSE 7名教授及學者，以及哈佛大學6名教授等等。<br />\n<br />\n聯署信中提到，有關判刑違反自由集會及表達的權利，亦同時違反《基本法》及政治權利國際公約及法治原則，要求中央及香港政府尊重港人政治權利及法治精神。<br />\n<br />\n■記者伍雅謙"},{"pid":"6e250911dcdc9428961ab3b1164790097f89a348","tid":401829,"uid":74918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:02:04.000Z","msg":"wfc <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快快手推過第二個做帶頭大哥仲好啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1fd06260fde1ff8ae0819f890bc7a9262d162e","tid":401829,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"幾年前同習近平鬥又唔支持佢,家下先支持有鬼用咩,劫獄丫笨"},{"pid":"c3e7358632da2305536115fc42d20846ce3bd339","tid":401829,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:11:26.000Z","msg":"呼籲全港愛國愛港人士抵制LSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n梁齊昕塊d撕爛LSE張畢業證書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79784753380e4a79772ba848db4a6414852684b","tid":401829,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:17:16.000Z","msg":"香港嘅大學：不認同學生違法行為"},{"pid":"007c78c117f546ccbee8d15b3068d8b7f865a869","tid":401829,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:21:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呼籲全港愛國愛港人士抵制LSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n梁齊昕塊d撕爛LSE張畢業證書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}